article.story: NASHVILLE, Tenn. -- — Will Pruitt's 23 points helped Lipscomb defeat Eastern Kentucky 81-67 on Friday night. Pruitt added 10 rebounds for the Bisons (20-11, 11-5 Atlantic Sun Conference). A.J McGinnis was 8 of 14 shooting (3 for 6 from 3-point range) to add 19 points. Cody Head had 12 points and finished 5 of 9 from the field. Leland Walker led the way for the Colonels (17-13, 12-4) with 21 points and two steals. Devontae Blanton added 12 points and nine rebounds for Eastern Kentucky. Isaiah Cozart also had 12 points, nine rebounds and four blocks. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
